projects.name: PG Life
projects.description: In PG Life is an online paying guest system, users can find several paying accommodations nearby the workplace or desired place. In this, user can get register to get a login id and password. With login id and password uses can get logged in. After logging in,the user can post paying guest post by adding details and pictures of the place. He/She can also view the interested users in his/her uploaded post.After selecting the desired place, the user will get the personal details of the owner,he/she get in contact with the owner and go for further processing.

projects.name: Event Labs
projects.description: Event labs is a platform designed to help in management of events. In this system we will provide authentication for workers and event organizers. Platform recognises and give information about the workers that are available and in under 5km radius. They also communicate with each other directly through chatting room.Chatbot is there for users assistance. In our tech stack, MongoDB shines as the guardian of our datasets, while the dynamic trio of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript handles the front-end magic. Meanwhile, behind the scenes, our API plays the role of the silent hero, orchestrating the backend symphony with finesse and precision.
